      6/23/83-7/26/84                       - 0.3
      8/20/87-12/3/87                       -25.0
   AVERAGE ANNUAL RETURN 6/30/80-6/30/90     21.1
                                                                                                       


                                                                                                       

   DOWN MARKETS
     11/20/80-2/19/81                       + 0.5
      6/11/81-9/24/81                       - 6.1
